          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Apply heatmap colors to graph view nodes.",
          "target": "为图谱视图中的节点应用热力图颜色。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "What drives the color. Time metrics (last modified, created) measure recency. Link metrics measure how connected a note is — useful for spotting hubs and orphans.",
          "target": "决定颜色的驱动因素。时间指标（最后修改、创建）衡量新近程度。链接指标衡量笔记的连接程度——有助于发现枢纽节点和孤立节点。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Relative: rank nodes by value, spread the gradient across the whole vault — every color is always used. Absolute: anchor the gradient to wall-clock age via 'Span (days)'. Absolute only applies to time metrics; link metrics always use relative.",
          "target": "相对：根据值对节点排序，将渐变色分布在整个库中——每种颜色都会被使用。绝对：通过“跨度（天）”将渐变色锚定到实际时间。绝对模式仅适用于时间指标；链接指标始终使用相对模式。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Pre-built palettes. Pick 'Custom' to define your own three stops below.",
          "target": "预设调色板。选择“自定义”以在下方定义您自己的三个色标。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Absolute mode only. Age at which a note is fully 'cold'. Older notes saturate at cold color.",
          "target": "仅限绝对模式。笔记完全“冷却”的年龄。更旧的笔记会饱和为冷色。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Compress the long tail — recent edits become more visually distinct.",
          "target": "压缩长尾分布——使近期编辑在视觉上更加突出。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Show the 'newest / oldest' or 'most / least' labels under the gradient swatch inside the controls panel.",
          "target": "在控制面板内的渐变色样下方显示“最新/最旧”或“最多/最少”标签。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Floating panel inside the graph view (bottom-left) with metric, scale, color preset, and gradient swatch — change everything without opening settings.",
          "target": "图谱视图内（左下角）的浮动面板，包含指标、比例、颜色预设和渐变色样——无需打开设置即可更改所有内容。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Theme = Obsidian's default. Dark / Light = a dark or light backdrop tinted with the active scale (pick whichever reads best for it). Auto = choose dark/light automatically for contrast. Custom = flat color.",
          "target": "主题 = Obsidian 默认。深色/浅色 = 使用活动比例着色的深色或浅色背景（选择可读性最佳的一种）。自动 = 自动选择深色/浅色以获得最佳对比度。自定义 = 纯色。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Theme = Obsidian's default. Custom = the flat color picked here. Heatmap = a color drawn from the active scale (its mid tone).",
          "target": "主题 = Obsidian 默认。自定义 = 此处选择的纯色。热力图 = 从活动比例中提取的颜色（其中间色调）。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "How visible the links are. Low (≈20%) keeps them subtle so the colored nodes stand out.",
          "target": "链接的可见度。低（≈20%）使其保持微妙，以便彩色节点更加突出。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "When Focus Mode is active, nodes that don't match the filter are dimmed by default (alpha 0.12). Turn this on to hide them and their edges completely.",
          "target": "当聚焦模式激活时，不匹配筛选条件的节点默认会变暗（透明度 0.12）。开启此项可完全隐藏它们及其边。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Highlight notes touched within the recency window below.",
          "target": "高亮显示在下方新近度窗口内被触及的笔记。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Glow blends the node color toward the marker color.",
          "target": "辉光将节点颜色向标记颜色混合。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Which timestamp decides 'recent' — when the note was last modified, or when it was created.",
          "target": "哪个时间戳决定“近期”——笔记最后修改的时间，还是创建的时间。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "How far back counts as 'recent'. e.g. 24 = last day, 168 = last week, 720 = last month.",
          "target": "多远的时间算作“近期”。例如 24 = 最近一天，168 = 最近一周，720 = 最近一个月。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Glow blends toward this color; outline draws the ring in it.",
          "target": "辉光向此颜色混合；轮廓用它绘制环。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "When hovering a node in the graph view, show its file path, the current metric's raw value, modification time, connection count, and rank within the vault.",
